 906:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  *
 907:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * If the IP address was already pending in the cache, a new ARP request
 908:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * is sent for the given address. The packet is queued on this entry.
