 920:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * q is not freed by this function.
 921:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  *
 922:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * @note q must only be ONE packet, not a packet queue!
 923:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  *
 924:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * @return
 925:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * - ERR_BUF Could not make room for Ethernet header.
 926:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * - ERR_MEM Hardware address unknown, and no more ARP entries available
 927:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  *   to query for address or queue the packet.
 928:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * - ERR_MEM Could not queue packet due to memory shortage.
 929:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * - ERR_RTE No route to destination (no gateway to external networks).
 930:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  * - ERR_ARG Non-unicast address given, those will not appear in ARP cache.
 931:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  *
 932:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/ipv4/etharp.c ****  */
